org.eclipse.gmt.modisco.java
Interface InfixExpression

All Superinterfaces:
ASTNode, Expression
public interface InfixExpression
extends Expression

A representation of the model object 'Infix Expression'.

The following features are supported:

  • Operator
  • Right Operand
  • Left Operand
  • Extended Operands
